him as rare and difficult to meet, and they will have veneration for him, perceive the sūtras he teaches to be the truth, and perceive them as something to be possessed and not to be maligned.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":282,\"end\":543}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"63f74c15-32b0-4ef0-9a98-b7b36f4389f4\",\"sort\":2018,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"2.24\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":230,\"uuid\":\"63f74c15-32b0-4ef0-9a98-b7b36f4389f4\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Therefore, noble one, because of those causes and conditions, the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":67}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tathāgata\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":67,\"end\":76},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e73562d6-15c5-4706-82c3-8f843ccfec58\",\"uuid\":\"b98ab553-87cb-490a-84b2-87e6a35a5f53\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" does not remain long in the world but quickly passes into \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":76,\"end\":135}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"nirvāṇa\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":135,\"end\":142},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bebe04fd-2b22-4637-89db-ae1cd69dffe1\",\"uuid\":\"8c94bf8b-7d0f-4f38-8e38-21d53ea12b69\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". It is through such a perfection of skillful methods that the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":142,\"end\":205}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"tathāgatas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":205,\"end\":215},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e73562d6-15c5-4706-82c3-8f843ccfec58\",\"uuid\":\"09b37a71-dd16-4434-bff8-b5201951701f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" ripen beings.”\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":215,\"end\":230}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"797ddc9b-9b27-4b44-b9d7-1f803803d377\",\"sort\":2026,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"2.25\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start